quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,176,"Garbô mari sinni farmoyta Nabii Shuqeybi dirabboyseeh, wohul Yallih farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  26,177,Nabii Shuqeybi Yallak mameesittaanaa?keenik iyye waqdi
  26,178,Diggah anu siinih amaanat-le farmoyta kinniyo edde rubsume diini sin gudduysaamal
  26,179,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola keenik iyye
  26,180,"Kaadu Yallih farmo sin gudduysaamal galtó sin messera, yi-galtó numul matanaay numul messera ginô Rabbil essera yoo akke waytek"
  26,181,"Nabii Shuqeybi keenik iyyeh: sinaamah tu-elle keexxan keelá duudusaay, keexó daggoysa mara makkina"
  26,182,Kaadu sinaamah massah yan miidaanay duddalel miidaanisa miidaanissaanam
  26,183,"Kaadu sinaamak-le cakki madaggoysinaay, baaxó mabaysina baaxó umaanet baysa mara tikki itteenih"
  26,184,Kaadu Yallay sin kee siinik naharsi ginoona gineh digaalák meesita
  26,185,"Madyan mari Nabii Shuqeybik :cagalah atu elle baaben marih num kinnito kaak iyyen"
  26,186,"Kaadu Shuqeybow atu ninnah yan seehadaytu akke waytek kalah tu hinnitooy, diggah nanu dirableelak numuk teyna koo nakkale kaak iyyen"
  26,187,Tokkel atu qaraanak digaalá kitiifoonuh nel oobis numma yacee marih num tekkek kaak iyyen
  26,188,Nabii Shuqeybi yi-Rabbi isin umaanek abba haytaanam yaaxigeh keenik iyye
  26,189,"Tokkel kaa dirabboyseeniih, gayrantuy ken silaalisa-le ayróh digaalá ken tibbixeeh ken finqisse, diggah woh kaxxa ayróh digaalá kinni"
  26,190,"Diggah too Nabii Shuqeybi marat tekke digaalát kaskassoowa marah astá tan, kaadu keenik maggo mari yeemene mara makko"
  26,191,Kaadu Nabii Mucammadow diggah ku-Rabbi usuk mayso-li xuwaw-li kinni